{"tid":795545,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得將電子競技項目加入奧運/亞運好憨鳩?","createTime":"2018-08-27T06:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T08:30:27.000Z","uid":163024,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95dd4d1b2ef98379f8da35b6840c1834a1a1aff4","tid":795545,"uid":163024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T06:03:42.000Z","msg":"今日又見到個亞運表演賽嘅新聞<br />\n玩傳說對決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我相信冇人會質疑電競嘅觀賞性同專業性(唔包括香港啲電莖選手同埋手機電莖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n但係我覺得啲人格硬要將電子競技歸類係「體育項目」度真係好撚柒鳩蠢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打機就打機，根本物理上嘅體育一啲關係都冇<br />\n依家外國電子競技嘅賽制同獎金池其實都已經比較成熟，但係台港澳啲蛋散就鍾意出黎鳩叫搞搞震<br />\n<br />\n你有冇見過啲人同你講要將圍棋、將琪、國際象棋加入奧運<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母電莖狗<br />\n棒球都俾人Del撚走咗幾時輪到你<br />\n<br />\n利申 LOL鑽石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4af570c5b9269bfbeb1771f4fa3a66b0c1617c4","tid":795545,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"成班肥臭毒撚係度打機叫運動<br />\n知唔知咩叫運動"},{"pid":"efc62a6be7902fe0d8e57ee4c6b7a8f7163d55b5","tid":795545,"uid":48887,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4af570c5b9269bfbeb1771f4fa3a66b0c1617c4","tid":795545,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:25:30.000Z","msg":"成班肥臭毒撚係度打機叫運動<br />\n知唔知咩叫運動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T08:30:27.000Z","msg":"肥臭毒撚郁下隻手已經算運動，強烈要求張打飛機都列入運動"}]}